{"tid":340899,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"濫用同音異字喺其中一個令語文水平下降原因","createTime":"2017-07-30T10:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T18:52:59.000Z","uid":2972,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c25f4923c081b9d0014a09393b9cb64a9f26e229","tid":340899,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無發覺<br />\n而家好多廣告、宣傳、劇名、電影名甚至牌子名都玩同音異字<br />\n即喺大家講嘅「食字」<br />\n其實食字呢樣古人吟詩作對已經玩唔少<br />\n而「食」得靚喺真可以表現到中文嘅言簡意賅<br />\n例如：有間賣鞋嘅舖叫喜有此履<br />\n我認為喺食得好靚<br />\n又例如而家好多泰國餐廳都鍾意用泰XX：泰好味、泰過癮⋯⋯呢啲都仲叫可以<br />\n<br />\n但而家實在太多亂嚟，為食字而食字嘅垃圾中文<br />\n而無綫可以話重災區<br />\n金枝「慾孽」、屈基、范統、丘玲梅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再近期啲嗰個乜鳩保濟Yeun...<br />\n完全不堪入耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而其實食字風咁盛行喺可以追溯到2003年<br />\n「茶」字典呢個廣告嘅出現<br />\n當時我仲喺中學雞<br />\n我中文阿Sir已經話呢啲廣告只會越嚟越多<br />\n亦只會越玩越爛<br />\n而家諗返真喺好啱<br />\n<br />\n咁鳩嗡咁耐到底想講乜<br />\n就喺呢種亂用同音異字嘅風已經好明顯影響到新一代<br />\n越嚟越多小學中學雞唔在意用字嘅精確<br />\n亦無人會深究到底有無錯別字<br />\n因為錯咗米當食字囉，仲可以笑吓添<br />\n我身邊亦有唔少朋友、同事喺咁<br />\n而我個人喺好撚憎錯別字<br />\n純粹想宣洩吓，同時希望巴打們要堅持用正字<br />\n可能嘅話就糾正身邊嘅人<br />\n鳩嗡完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b41f8e16e69a3e77ac8c47f6c2509d98183a72","tid":340899,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"Ching高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca25efaed1ac8d5fedd4c6687cdac93068eba1ab","tid":340899,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"語文水平下降係因為用左西方學拼音文字果一套學習方法。"},{"pid":"7854eb297f86564ffc92bb62eb77dc91ddd8797d","tid":340899,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6234ca8287597284f803e87bb97c1d3480741d79","tid":340899,"uid":79686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:40:45.000Z","msg":"所以5p字真係要屌"},{"pid":"eb3ebffefec8ae15c9b55196e0a67c6d5d971598","tid":340899,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>語文水平下降係因為用左西方學拼音文字果一套學習方法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗原因好多，所以我話喺其中一個"},{"pid":"40fcc09d22d0b5bb71be880cea8263741c8fc110","tid":340899,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6bab4d246357cd9ad30986a349dcc11581d9ef01","tid":340899,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以5p字真係要屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，尤其連登真喺重災區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad916388952d51f1f560bbad99c681a1e5b64c21","tid":340899,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以5p字真係要屌</blockquote><br />\n見撚到啲「挽」「汁」就憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c91e1ed8c61f6cb54393719555d24041f2b42c6","tid":340899,"uid":2972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T18:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以5p字真係要屌</blockquote><br />\n見撚到啲「挽」「汁」就憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯，見到好撚燥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2772b5c822c64af87cec425ed7e4fb4af2fbb257"